Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:52.24,Shiver,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur0.6\pos(200,20)}Everything that was right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:55.06,Shiver,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur0.6\pos(630,20)}We both enjoyed a good fight
