Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:54.44,Shiver,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur0.6\pos(30,20)}Just for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:02:02.02,Shiver,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur0.6\pos(30,20)}Like I used to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't take much more of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When will it finally rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to divine when the rains will come?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be blessed by rain in two days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bring the jugs out! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Her divination came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:42.58,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\fad(2000,0)\an7\bord0\blur0.6\p1\c&H8C4863&\pos(-2,68)\fscx380\fscy90}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 2,0:03:36.61,0:03:42.58,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\an4\fad(2000,0)\blur0.6\pos(58,110)}Cloudless Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Water that soaks not into the earth but instead creeps along its surface
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is but an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though you may pursue it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you will never reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Praying for rain, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the weather seems unwilling to provide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of any watering holes around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to replenish my supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should spend a few days here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The rains will soon come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She smelled of rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The heavens will soon bless us with rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Teru!{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Miss Teru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please rest at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us hold a banquet tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all welcome to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a traveler passing through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you spare me some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. We don't have enough right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But it will rain soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever that girl foretells rain, it rains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She has never been wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rather curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. There's a big puddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a mirage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how fast you run, \Nyou'll never catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's try anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Teru! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm digging a well there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The one in the village always dries up during summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can take a break once the rain is here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you go away again when that happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd rather travel around all by yourself instead of settling down here with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't plan on living in any one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then at least come by more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You decided to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious to see how you'll make it rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I only came here to foretell the rain's arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think anyone is capable of {\i1}causing{\i0} the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No normal person could.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone able to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,would no longer be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Teru, rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessed rain!{same phrase as in the first scene}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,An epidemic's broken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because of this ceaseless rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When will this rain... finally end?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryou—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to howl and cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I can't even shed a tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your aunt has agreed to take care of you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no more food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Once things improve,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you can live here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What horrible rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that girl's home village devastated by rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If this keeps up, we'll suffer the same fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though she brought the rain with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The village is back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's as though she brought the rain with her.{ouch}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:13:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know how this happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I know is that I have no home to return to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and no place I can make my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't even have tears I can shed to accept that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have food from our stockpile, \Nso it's nothing special, but please help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you save the celebrations until after the rain comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't want to wait anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is today too early to hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miss Teru, do you think it'll be much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll come very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Normally it would be here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still no rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What could be the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd better finish the well soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder! Please let us talk to Miss Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll rain very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How many days have you been saying {\i1}that{\i0} for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We've used up all our water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Can anyone spare a little more water?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No... That was the last we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain! When will it rain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Te... ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'll rain soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasu, just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll bring you some water right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look too happy, \Neven though it rained just like you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you still need something from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed something while watching you over the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in this heat, I haven't seen a single drop of sweat on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing you can't shed tears either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I wish I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, have you ever caught something you shouldn't have been able to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something I shouldn't have been able to catch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Teru, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! That puddle isn't running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the puddle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you. It was a mirage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The mirage...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That is one form of the Amefurashi, or "Rainmaker" mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They normally hang suspended in air like fine water droplets,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but they fall to the ground once they gather enough moisture to cause rain to form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they return to the air as the water evaporates
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and gather rain again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But when the land is stricken by drought and there is no moisture in the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they pool near the ground's surface \Nand take on a mirage-like appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Aside from the fact that they are alive, \Nthey are essentially a natural phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We call such mushi "drifters."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They wander without a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When you came in contact with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they took over the moisture within your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And now they continually rise from you, gathering rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They did all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them out of my body at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no treatment for drifters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only wait for their lifespan to reach an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When will that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's taking longer for the rain to appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it may mean that they are weakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to despair about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This rain of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,has claimed the lives of many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I almost killed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You will have to shoulder the burden of those lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were not at fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and neither were the Amefurashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just an unfortunate twist of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you've already figured out a relatively good way to coexist with the Amefurashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's not {\i1}all{\i0} bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Teru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once the rain stops
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I can shed true tears again,{sup futsuu}{PLS}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.03,0:21:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will put down roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will continue to drift like the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with the rain by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel alive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange rain, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:22:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, but it's beautiful all the same.
